The results for [[1898 Glamorgan County Council election|1898]] and [[1901 Glamorgan County Council election|1901]] are unavailable but by [[1904 Glamorgan County Council election|1904]], Luther Davies, a manager at the Aberaman Colliery had taken over as the county councillor for Aberaman.

