Despite the challenge of the [[Labour Party (UK)|Labour Party]] at district council level, including a significant impact at Aberaman (see below), labour did not challenge for the county seat in this period.

===Aberdare Urban District Council===
Aberaman was also an electoral ward of the [[Aberdare Urban District Council]] from its formation in 1894.

