==21st century==
Aberaman currently has two wards, Aberaman North and Aberaman South for the purposes of [[Rhondda Cynon Taf]] unitary authority elections. Since 1995 it has been represented by [[Plaid Cymru]] and [[Labour Party (UK)|Labour]] councillors.

